if heavy rain in next 48 hours:
    Daily text that lists rain incidents

Every 24 hours:
    if heavy rain in the next 48 hours:
        Send text that lists rain incidents
        mark all incidents as notified

Every hour:
    Check for heavy rain in next 24 hours
        if weather is found that is 
            not in notified list:
            
            if day:
                if weather is less than 2 hours away
                    call
                    mark as notified
                else 
                    text
                    mark as notified
            else: #night
                if weather is before daytime:
                    call
                    mark as notified
                else:
                    # do nothing; include on next daily report
                    do not mark as notified